comment: Adams (OKC) grabs and holds Embiid's (PHI) arm affecting his ability to contest Roberson's (OKC) drive to the basket.
Embiid (PHI) makes contact to the body of Roberson (OKC) and affects his driving shot attempt.
LHH shows Covington (PHI) cleanly strips the shot attempt by Roberson (OKC).
Covington (PHI) and Roberson (OKC) both have their hands on the ball when Roberson returns to the floor and it is a held ball.
Embiid (PHI) maintains legal guarding position and absorbs the contact initiated by Westbrook (OKC) on the drive.
Roberson (OKC) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Rodriguez (PHI).
Henderson (PHI) makes contact with Westbrook (OKC) that affects his SQBR.
Adams (OKC) maintains legal guarding position while defending Embiid (PHI) in the post.
LHH shows Adams (OKC) maintains legal guarding position and makes contact with Embiid's (PHI) hand when it is considered part of the ball.
Henderson (PHI) sets the screen on Oladipo (OKC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Westbrook (OKC) maintains legal guarding position and cleanly makes contact with the ball on the drive by Henderson (PHI).
RATR shows Roberson (OKC) maintains legal guarding position and cleanly blocks Henderson's (PHI) shot.
Embiid (PHI) cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt by Oladipo (OKC).
Westbrook (OKC) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Embiid (PHI) on the perimeter.
Westbrook (OKC) strips the ball from Embiid (PHI) prior to him lifting his pivot foot.
Oladipo (OKC) establishes legal guarding position outside of the RA and absorbs the contact from Embiid (PHI).
After communicating with the Replay Center, it was confirmed that Oladipo (OKC) established position outside of the RA when contact occurs.
Covington (PHI) commits a take foul on Oladipo (OKC).
